title: The Bounce - Wrap Cover Pack (Image|2013-14|Digital''300|Empire)
description:
Overview:


  <a href=" http://imagecomics.com/content/view/a-superhero-for-the-21st-century-in-the-bounce" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://imagecomics.com/content/view/a-superhero-for-the-21st-century-in-the-bounce</a>



Contains:


   The Bounce 001-012 (2013-2014) (Wrap Cover) (Digital''300) (Darkness-Empire).jpg

   Each issue of this series was supposed to have a wrap cover, but more than half
   the Empire releases included only the two separated halves in front and back. I
   stuck 'em back together.
   
   As an unanticipated side benefit, there is a kind of extra dimension to some of
   the peripheral graphical elements here, which only becomes readily apparent when
   one flicks through them in direct succession. So, have fun playing with that! :)
